#################
  HOW TO RUN
#################

The 'openshot' file in the /bin/ folder is meant to be copied
to the /usr/bin/ folder. 

$ sudo python setup.py install

After you install OpenShot with this command, it should have
an icon in the Applications menu, and the following command
should run OpenShot from anywhere on the computer:  $ openshot
